    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Clean, honest car that\u2019s ready to be a solid daily driver for someone who wants dependable transportation without breaking the bank. It shows the kind of normal wear you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle, but it still has plenty of life left and drives well. A great fit for a first car, commuter, or anyone looking for practical value. Priced fairly and worth a look.",
