      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Well-kept driver with strong mechanical character and a confident road feel. Starts clean, pulls smoothly through the rev range, and delivers the kind of solid, dependable performance that makes it easy to enjoy every day. The powertrain feels healthy, the chassis tracks straight, and it has clearly benefited from consistent upkeep over time. Cosmetically it shows normal age-related wear, but overall it presents as an honest, capable vehicle with plenty of life left. Great option for someone who wants a practical, enjoyable car without paying premium-tier money.",
